{"tid":2315164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中大遊行】律師稱警方以非法集結拘捕楊子雋 未涉國安罪名","createTime":"2020-12-07T04:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T05:14:17.000Z","uid":244704,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0f90a4ca5de07f9a6cd2bfe0f207eee55e49fbfe","tid":2315164,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:41:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>律師稱警方以非法集結拘捕楊子雋 未涉國安罪名</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n　　消息指，警方國安處拘捕8人，包括中大畢業生楊子雋、陳易舜和李嘉睿，懷疑與上月中大遊行有關。<br />\n<br />\n　　本身是中大校友的「灣仔起步」成員楊子雋被送往大埔警署，他的社交網站引述律師指，警方以「非法集結」罪拘捕他，暫時未有國家安全相關的罪名。觀塘區議員陳易舜的社交網站就指，陳易舜早上被警方帶到觀塘警署，有律師陪同。西貢區議員李嘉睿社交網站就指，他清晨6時被警方上門帶走，律師正了解中。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2369577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2369577&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTkBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=07b29189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2369577</a>"},{"pid":"09416cbb204d8e7ca3ea7924b4e2c3cae40dfd7c","tid":2315164,"uid":82938,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢d政治人物黎<br />\n關乜事<br />\n<br />\n又用國安法告非法集結唔比保釋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3580f968165a2c0d0492c1473c4671d1ca1cb4c2","tid":2315164,"uid":279938,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:45:48.000Z","msg":"大學裡面告非法集結喎"},{"pid":"f65efe5c928aa760260b28628ad11d72a7ee2083","tid":2315164,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"09416cbb204d8e7ca3ea7924b4e2c3cae40dfd7c","tid":2315164,"uid":82938,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"